Crotale follows suit of Crossroads as he to walks out of the base.  
"Interesting.  You sure we can trust him, Pacifix, he does look 
rather primitive."  Lokking smugly at the elephant Crotale steps 
forward, hands resting calmy, yet showing a bit of tenseness, on 
his chain guns.  "Welcome to our ranks.  The name is Crotale.  Let 
it be known I do not trust, people who just pop up.  I'll have my 
sensors on you. " Turning swiftly he walked back towards the ship. 
 As he passes Pacifix he whispers into his ear.  "Don't be so quick 
to trust him Pacifix.  I know you already do though." He then 
walked calmly to his quaters, his radars picking up most of 
Skullhammers direct actions.
----------------------------------------------

JetV recieved his transmission.  "Got it boss." he said diving under 
the blue depths and racing back up to the surface.  Shooting out of 
the water he landed on the sandy beach, not as a JetSki and more 
but as an ATV.  In a puff of dust he peels off across the dunes.
